## ğŸ”§ **REST API Reference**

### **Base URL Structure**
```
http://localhost:5000/          # API information
http://localhost:5000/health    # Health check
http://localhost:5000/api/      # All blog endpoints
```

### **Authentication**
All API endpoints (except `/` and `/health`) require authentication:

```bash
curl -H "X-API-Key: your_api_key" http://localhost:5000/api/posts
```

### **Standard Response Format**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "timestamp": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000000Z",
  "data": {
    // Response data here
  }
}
```

### **âš ï¸ TIMEOUT CONFIGURATION NOTICE**
- **Image Generation Endpoints**: `/api/posts` (with `use_generated_feature_image: true`) and `/api/posts/{id}/image` require extended timeouts
- **Recommended Client Timeout**: **5 minutes (300 seconds)** minimum
- **Typical Response Times**: 60-300 seconds for image generation
- **Without Images**: Standard 30-second timeout is sufficient

### **ğŸ“ Core Endpoints**

#### Create Blog Post âš ï¸ **Extended Timeout for Images**
```bash
POST /api/posts
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: your_api_key

{
  "title": "My Blog Post",
  "content": "Post content in **Markdown**",
  "excerpt": "Brief summary",
  "tags": ["Tag1", "Tag2"],
  "status": "published",
  "use_generated_feature_image": true,
  "prefer_flux": true,
  "image_aspect_ratio": "16:9"
}
```

**â±ï¸ Important:** When `use_generated_feature_image: true` is used, generation can take 60-300 seconds. Set client timeout to at least **5 minutes (300 seconds)**.

#### Smart Create (AI-Enhanced)
```bash
POST /api/smart-create
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: your_api_key

{
  "user_input": "Write about AI benefits in healthcare",
  "status": "draft",
  "preferred_language": "English"
}
```

#### Get Posts
```bash
GET /api/posts?limit=5&status=published&featured=true
X-API-Key: your_api_key
```

#### Update Post Image âš ï¸ **High Timeout Required**
```bash
PUT /api/posts/{post_id}/image
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: your_api_key

{
  "use_generated_feature_image": true,
  "prefer_imagen": true,
  "image_aspect_ratio": "16:9"
}
```

**â±ï¸ Important:** Image generation endpoints can take 60-300 seconds to complete. Set client timeout to at least **5 minutes (300 seconds)** for reliable operation.

### **ğŸ“‹ Complete Endpoint List**

| Endpoint | Method | Description | Auth Required | Timeout |
|----------|--------|-------------|---------------|---------|
| `/` | GET | API information | âŒ | Standard |
| `/health` | GET | Health check | âŒ | Standard |
| `/api/posts` | POST | Create blog post | âœ… | **Extended*** |
| `/api/smart-create` | POST | AI-enhanced creation | âœ… | Standard |
| `/api/posts` | GET | List posts | âœ… | Standard |
| `/api/posts/advanced` | GET | Advanced search | âœ… | Standard |
| `/api/posts/{id}` | GET | Get post details | âœ… | Standard |
| `/api/posts/{id}` | PUT/PATCH | Update post | âœ… | Standard |
| `/api/posts/{id}` | DELETE | Delete post | âœ… | Standard |
| `/api/posts/{id}/image` | PUT | Update post image | âœ… | **Extended*** |
| `/api/posts/summary` | GET | Posts summary | âœ… | Standard |
| `/api/posts/batch-details` | POST | Batch get details | âœ… | Standard |
| `/api/posts/search/by-date-pattern` | GET | Date search | âœ… | Standard |

**\*Extended = 5 minutes (300 seconds) for image generation**

---

## â±ï¸ **Performance & Timeout Guidelines**

### **Image Generation Performance**
- **Replicate Flux**: 3-7 seconds (ultra-fast)
- **Google Imagen**: 10-15 seconds (professional quality)
- **Upload & Processing**: Additional 45-60 seconds
- **Total Time**: 60-300 seconds for complete image generation

### **Recommended Client Timeouts**
```javascript
// For endpoints WITH image generation
const imageApiTimeout = 300000; // 5 minutes

// For endpoints WITHOUT image generation  
const standardTimeout = 30000; // 30 seconds
```

### **Production Testing Results**
âœ… **All endpoints functional**  
âš ï¸ **Image generation requires extended timeout**  
ğŸ’¡ **Recommendation**: Always set 5-minute timeout for image endpoints

